<strong>AO Tennis 2</strong> is a video game released in the beginning of 2020. It supports playing online if you have Playstation Plus account. Besides the gameplay, Playstation also provides camera and microphone to broadcast how the players were reacting every game. Although we have a little difficulties on the connection (disconnected), the overall experience was good.</p>
